=== Major rituals ===
* Jan 1: Saitansai / New Year's festival
* Feb 10: Mikuwa festival
* Old lunar Feb 14: Akiba festival
* Third Sunday of Feb: Kinen-sai
* Mar 15: Sumiyoshi festival
* First Saturday of Apr: Okunomiya festival and Suijin festival
* First Sunday of Apr: Chinka-sai
* Jun 30: Summer purification
* Oct (second Sunday): Grand festival
* Nov (fourth Sunday): Niiname-sai
* Dec 30: Year-end purification
* Dec 31: Joya festival
* Monthly: 1st day and 15th day rites

